cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.LG 

This paper focuses on generating characteristic comments for fashion photos, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and machine learning for natural language processing. The second likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which covers image captioning and image analysis. The third likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), which covers social media analysis and user engagement. The fourth likely sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which covers multimedia analysis and retrieval. The fifth likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers machine learning techniques used in the proposed framework.
